    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="tm-legend">
  <span><span class="tm-scan">盤查</span> 完成溫室氣體盤查</span>
  <span><span class="tm-conf">確信</span> 完成第三方確信</span>
  <span style="color:var(--gray);font-size:.72rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 原則：先個體後合併，先盤查後確信</span>
</div>
</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch2"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch2-tag">第二章</span><h3>GRI / SASB / TCFD 框架比較</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<div style="overflow-x:auto;"><table class="fw-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="width:22%;background:#607d8b;">比較項目</th>
      <th style="width:26%;background:#2e7a52;">GRI</th>
      <th style="width:26%;background:#89b4d4;">SASB</th>
      <th style="width:26%;background:#c87848;">TCFD</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="fw-row-label">主要受眾</td>
      <td><b>多方利害關係人</b><br><small>（非只投資人）</small></td>
      <td><b>投資人</b><br><small>資本市場為核心</small></td>
      <td><b>投資人 ／ 金融機構</b></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="fw-row-label">重大性</td>
      <td>影響重大性<br><small>企業對外的衝擊</small></td>
      <td>財務重大性<br><small>對企業財務的影響</small></td>
      <td>氣候財務重大性</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="fw-row-label">適用範圍</td>
      <td>任何產業均可</td>
      <td>77項行業別<br><small>（產業特定指標）</small></td>
      <td>所有組織</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="fw-row-label">核心特色</td>
      <td>全面性揭露<br>正負面衝擊均需揭露</td>
      <td>三大特色：<br>指標一致性<br>產業特定<br>指標可比性</td>
      <td>四大支柱：<br>治理、策略<br>風險管理<br>指標與目標</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="fw-row-label">方向比喻</td>
      <td>由內而外<br><small>企業影響世界</small></td>
      <td>由外而內<br><small>世界影響企業財務</small></td>
      <td>氣候視角</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="fw-row-label">台灣法規要求</td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg> 永續報告書<br>依GRI準則編製</td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg> 2025年起<br>全體上市櫃參考</td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg> 股東會年報<br>氣候資訊揭露</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table></div>
<div class="fw-must"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg> 考點：IFRS S1/S2 同時參考 <b>TCFD</b> 四大構面 + <b>SASB</b> 產業特定指引</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> GRI對象是多方利害關係人（非只投資人）；SASB以投資人為核心，具產業特定性；TCFD聚焦氣候財務揭露</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch2"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch2-tag">第二章</span><h3>溫室氣體三大範疇</h3></div><div class="chart-body"><div class="scope-boxes"><div class="scope-box sb1"><div class="sb-num">範疇一</div><div class="sb-name">直接排放</div><div class="sb-emoji"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#546e7a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M2 20V8l6 4V8l6 4V8l6 4v8H2z"/><line x1="2" y1="20" x2="22" y2="20"/></svg></div><div class="sb-items">工廠煙囪<br>公務車輛<br>冷媒逸散</div><div class="sb-tag">「自家煙囪」</div></div><div class="scope-arrow">→</div><div class="scope-box sb2"><div class="sb-num">範疇二</div><div class="sb-name">能源間接</div><div class="sb-emoji"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="#d4a56a" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg></div><div class="sb-items">外購電力<br>外購蒸汽</div><div class="sb-tag">「繳電費的」</div></div><div class="scope-arrow">→</div><div class="scope-box sb3"><div class="sb-num">範疇三</div><div class="sb-name">其他間接</div><div class="sb-emoji"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg></div><div class="sb-items">員工通勤/出差<br>供應商碳排<br>產品廢棄</div><div class="sb-tag">「別人的業障」</div></div></div></div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 冷媒逸散＝範疇一；出差搭高鐵＝範疇三</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch2"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch2-tag">第二章</span><h3>ISSB 成立沿革時間軸</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.issb-tl{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;}
.issb-item{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:stretch;}
.issb-dot-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;width:36px;flex-shrink:0;}
.issb-dot{width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:5px;}
.issb-line{width:2px;flex:1;background:#b8e4d0;margin:3px 0;}
.issb-body{padding:7px 0 12px;flex:1;}
.issb-year{font-size:.82rem;font-weight:800;color:#1b5c42;}
.issb-desc{font-size:.74rem;color:#37474f;line-height:1.6;margin-top:2px;}
.issb-tag{display:inline-block;padding:1px 7px;border-radius:8px;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;}
</style>
<div class="issb-tl">
  <div class="issb-item">
    <div class="issb-dot-col"><div class="issb-dot" style="background:#72c49a;"></div><div class="issb-line"></div></div>
    <div class="issb-body"><div class="issb-year">2021.6 <span class="issb-tag" style="background:#e2f5ec;color:#2e7a52;">SASB + IIRC 合併</span></div><div class="issb-desc">成立<b>價值報告基金會（VRF）</b>，整合 SASB 準則、&lt;IR&gt; 整合報告架構、整合性思維原則</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="issb-item">
    <div class="issb-dot-col"><div class="issb-dot" style="background:#3fa068;"></div><div class="issb-line"></div></div>
    <div class="issb-body"><div class="issb-year">2021.11 <span class="issb-tag" style="background:#fdf0e0;color:#c87848;">COP26 宣布</span></div><div class="issb-desc">IFRS 基金會宣布成立 <b>ISSB（國際永續準則理事會）</b><br>同時宣布將 VRF 及 CDSB 併入 IFRS Foundation</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="issb-item">
    <div class="issb-dot-col"><div class="issb-dot" style="background:#2e7a52;"></div><div class="issb-line"></div></div>
    <div class="issb-body"><div class="issb-year">2022 <span class="issb-tag" style="background:#e8f2f9;color:#89b4d4;">正式運作</span></div><div class="issb-desc">ISSB 開始運作，制定永續揭露準則草案</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="issb-item">
    <div class="issb-dot-col"><div class="issb-dot" style="background:#1b5c42;"></div></div>
    <div class="issb-body"><div class="issb-year">2023.6 <span class="issb-tag" style="background:#e2f5ec;color:#1b5c42;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg> 正式發布</span></div><div class="issb-desc">發布 <b>IFRS S1</b>（永續相關財務資訊一般揭露）<br>發布 <b>IFRS S2</b>（氣候相關揭露，整合TCFD架構）</div></div>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> ISSB 由 COP26 宣布；S1 通用準則、S2 氣候專項；整合了 TCFD、SASB 等既有框架</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch2"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch2-tag">第二章</span><h3>台灣接軌 IFRS 永續揭露準則藍圖</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.ifrs-tl{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
.ifrs-row{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;}
.ifrs-year{width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:800;font-size:.78rem;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
.ifrs-box{flex:1;border-radius:10px;padding:9px 12px;font-size:.74rem;line-height:1.6;}
.ifrs-box b{display:block;font-size:.8rem;margin-bottom:2px;}
.ifrs-arrow{font-size:1rem;color:#aaa;flex-shrink:0;}
</style>
<div class="ifrs-tl">
  <div class="ifrs-row">
    <div class="ifrs-year" style="background:#89b4d4;">2026</div>
    <div class="ifrs-box" style="background:#e8f2f9;border:1.5px solid #90caf9;">
      <b style="color:#89b4d4;">第一階段</b>
      資本額 <b>100億元以上</b> 上市櫃公司<br>
      <small style="color:#546e7a;">首年僅需揭露氣候議題（S2）；免揭露比較期間資訊</small>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ifrs-row">
    <div class="ifrs-year" style="background:#89b4d4;">2027</div>
    <div class="ifrs-box" style="background:#e8eaf6;border:1.5px solid #9fa8da;">
      <b style="color:#283593;">第二階段</b>
      資本額 <b>50～100億元</b> 上市櫃公司<br>
      <small style="color:#546e7a;">範疇三排放延後一年揭露</small>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ifrs-row">
    <div class="ifrs-year" style="background:#1b5c42;">2028</div>
    <div class="ifrs-box" style="background:#e2f5ec;border:1.5px solid #b8e4d0;">
      <b style="color:#1b5c42;">第三階段</b>
      <b>所有其餘上市櫃公司</b><br>
      <small style="color:#546e7a;">全面適用 IFRS S1 + S2</small>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 台灣採直接採用（非自訂）；揭露位置：年報永續資訊專章，與財務報告同時公告</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch2"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch2-tag">第二章</span><h3>確信等級：合理 vs 有限</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.assur-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;}
.assur-box{border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;}
.assur-head{padding:9px 14px;font-weight:800;font-size:.84rem;color:#fff;text-align:center;}
.assur-body{padding:12px 14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;}
.assur-row{display:flex;gap:8px;font-size:.75rem;line-height:1.5;}
.assur-icon{flex-shrink:0;font-size:.9rem;}
.assur-trap{font-size:.7rem;color:#b71c1c;background:#ffebee;border-radius:5px;padding:2px 7px;margin-top:4px;display:inline-block;}
.assur-rea .assur-head{background:#1b5c42;}
.assur-rea .assur-body{background:#e2f5ec;}
.assur-lim .assur-head{background:#89b4d4;}
.assur-lim .assur-body{background:#e8f2f9;}
</style>
<div class="assur-grid">
  <div class="assur-box assur-rea">
    <div class="assur-head"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg> 合理確信（Reasonable）</div>
    <div class="assur-body">
      <div class="assur-row"><span class="assur-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg></span><div>查核程序<b>廣泛</b>（詳細查驗）</div></div>
      <div class="assur-row"><span class="assur-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg></span><div><b>正面措辭</b>結論<br>「報告書未含重大不實表達」</div></div>
      <div class="assur-row"><span class="assur-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#d4a56a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M9.5 4h5L17 8H7l2.5-4z"/><path d="M7 8a5 5 0 0 0 10 0"/><path d="M12 8v4"/><path d="M7 13h10l1 9H6l1-9z"/></svg></span><div>費用較高、時間較長</div></div>
      <span class="assur-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 正面語氣 = 合理確信</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="assur-box assur-lim">
    <div class="assur-head"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#89b4d4" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8" fill="#89b4d4" stroke="none"/></svg> 有限確信（Limited）</div>
    <div class="assur-body">
      <div class="assur-row"><span class="assur-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg></span><div>查核程序<b>有限</b>（詢問+分析）</div></div>
      <div class="assur-row"><span class="assur-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg></span><div><b>負面措辭</b>結論<br>「未發現重大不實表達」</div></div>
      <div class="assur-row"><span class="assur-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#d4a56a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M9.5 4h5L17 8H7l2.5-4z"/><path d="M7 8a5 5 0 0 0 10 0"/><path d="M12 8v4"/><path d="M7 13h10l1 9H6l1-9z"/></svg></span><div>費用較低、適合初期導入</div></div>
      <span class="assur-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 負面語氣 = 有限確信</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 兩者均依 ISAE 3000/3410 準則；差異在於程序廣泛程度與結論語氣（正面 vs 負面）</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch2"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch2-tag">第二章</span><h3>TNFD LEAP 方法四步驟</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.leap-flow{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;}
.leap-item{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:stretch;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;}
.leap-letter{width:44px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:900;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
.leap-content{flex:1;padding:10px 12px;font-size:.75rem;line-height:1.6;}
.leap-content b{font-size:.82rem;display:block;margin-bottom:2px;}
.leap-trap{font-size:.69rem;color:#b71c1c;background:#ffebee;border-radius:4px;padding:1px 6px;display:inline-block;margin-top:3px;}
</style>
<div class="leap-flow">
  <div class="leap-item">
    <div class="leap-letter" style="background:#2e7a52;">L</div>
    <div class="leap-content" style="background:#e2f5ec;">
      <b style="color:#1b5c42;">Locate（定位）</b>
      找出組織在自然界中的位置——供應鏈、營運地點與自然的介面<br>
      <span class="leap-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> L = 在哪裡</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="leap-item">
    <div class="leap-letter" style="background:#89b4d4;">E</div>
    <div class="leap-content" style="background:#e8f2f9;">
      <b style="color:#5a8ab8;">Evaluate（評價）</b>
      了解組織對自然的<b>依賴（Dependency）和影響（Impact）</b><br>
      <span class="leap-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> E = 依賴和影響</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="leap-item">
    <div class="leap-letter" style="background:#c87848;">A</div>
    <div class="leap-content" style="background:#fdf0e0;">
      <b style="color:#b86840;">Assess（評估）</b>
      識別組織面臨的自然相關<b>風險（Risk）和機會（Opportunity）</b>並排序<br>
      <span class="leap-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> A = 風險和機會</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="leap-item">
    <div class="leap-letter" style="background:#8872b8;">P</div>
    <div class="leap-content" style="background:#ede8f7;">
      <b style="color:#4a148c;">Prepare（準備）</b>
      使用 LEAP 評估結果，與利害關係人討論，制定<b>因應策略與揭露</b><br>
      <span class="leap-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> P = 策略與揭露</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> TNFD = 自然版的TCFD；E = 依賴/影響（不是風險）；A = 風險/機會（不是評價）</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch3"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch3-tag">第三章</span><h3>TCFD 氣候風險分類</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.risk-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;}
.risk-box{border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;}
.risk-box-head{padding:8px 12px;font-weight:800;font-size:.82rem;color:#fff;}
.risk-box-body{padding:10px 12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;}
.risk-row{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:.76rem;line-height:1.5;}
.risk-row-icon{font-size:.9rem;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
.risk-row-content b{color:#263238;display:block;font-size:.76rem;}
.risk-row-content small{color:#546e7a;font-size:.7rem;}
.risk-trap{font-size:.7rem;color:#b71c1c;background:#ffebee;border-radius:5px;padding:2px 7px;display:inline-block;margin-top:1px;}
/* transition */
.risk-trans .risk-box-head{background:#c87848;}
.risk-trans .risk-box-body{background:#fdf0e0;}
/* physical */
.risk-phys-a .risk-box-head{background:#89b4d4;}
.risk-phys-a .risk-box-body{background:#e8f2f9;}
.risk-phys-b .risk-box-head{background:#1b5c42;}
.risk-phys-b .risk-box-body{background:#e2f5ec;}
.risk-full{grid-column:1/-1;}
</style>
<div class="risk-grid">
  <!-- 轉型風險 -->
  <div class="risk-box risk-trans risk-full" style="display:block;">
    <div class="risk-box-head"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/><polyline points="1 20 1 14 7 14"/><path d="M3.51 9a9 9 0 0 1 14.85-3.36L23 10M1 14l4.64 4.36A9 9 0 0 0 20.49 15"/></svg> 轉型風險（Transition Risk）— 向低碳經濟轉型過程中的風險</div>
    <div class="risk-box-body" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4px;">
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1" ry="1"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>法規與政策</b><small>碳費開徵、燃油車禁令、碳稅</small><span class="risk-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 碳費開徵 = 轉型風險，非實體</span></div></div>
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="2" y1="20" x2="22" y2="20"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>技術</b><small>開發低碳技術導致成本提升</small></div></div>
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>市場</b><small>消費偏好轉向、原物料價格上漲</small></div></div>
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>名譽</b><small>漂綠爭議、ESG評分下降影響募資</small></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- 實體風險 - 立即性 -->
  <div class="risk-box risk-phys-a">
    <div class="risk-box-head"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="#d4a56a" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg> 立即性實體風險（Acute）</div>
    <div class="risk-box-body">
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#4a9480" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 1 10 10c0 4-2.3 7.4-5.6 9.1"/><path d="M12 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6c0 2.4-1.4 4.5-3.4 5.5"/><path d="M12 14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 .8-.5 1.5-1.2 1.8"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>以單一事件為主</b><small>颱風、龍捲風、洪水、乾旱</small></div></div>
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#89b4d4" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M12 2.69l5.66 5.66a8 8 0 1 1-11.31 0z"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>例：缺雨</b><small>對水資源依賴高之企業衝擊大</small></div></div>
      <span class="risk-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 颱風損壞廠房 = 立即性</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- 實體風險 - 長期性 -->
  <div class="risk-box risk-phys-b">
    <div class="risk-box-head"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"/></svg> 長期性實體風險（Chronic）</div>
    <div class="risk-box-body">
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M2 6c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1C7 7 7 5 9.5 5c2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1"/><path d="M2 12c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1"/><path d="M2 18c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>氣候模式的長期變化</b><small>海平面上升、夏季增長</small></div></div>
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>例：海平面上升</b><small>沿海房價預期下跌 = 長期性</small></div></div>
      <div class="risk-row"><span class="risk-row-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#4e342e" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></span><div class="risk-row-content"><b>例：土壤劣化</b><small>農作物生產力下降 = 長期性</small></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 「碳費開徵」「技術替代」= 轉型風險 ｜「颱風損壞廠房」= 立即性實體 ｜「海平面上升房價跌」= 長期性實體</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch3"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch3-tag">第三章</span><h3>溫室氣體：管制範圍對照</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.ghg-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.75rem;}
.ghg-tbl th{padding:7px 10px;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:.73rem;text-align:center;}
.ghg-tbl td{padding:7px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;font-size:.73rem;line-height:1.5;text-align:center;}
.ghg-tbl tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}
.ghg-yes{color:#1b5c42;font-weight:700;}
.ghg-no{color:#b71c1c;}
.ghg-trap{font-size:.7rem;color:#b71c1c;background:#ffebee;border-radius:4px;padding:1px 6px;}
</style>
<table class="ghg-tbl">
  <thead><tr>
    <th style="background:#37474f;text-align:left;padding-left:14px;">溫室氣體</th>
    <th style="background:#1b5c42;">氣候變遷因應法<br><small>（台灣7種）</small></th>
    <th style="background:#89b4d4;">IPCC AR6<br><small>（預測關鍵驅動）</small></th>
  </tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">CO₂ 二氧化碳</td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td></tr>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">CH₄ 甲烷</td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td></tr>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">N₂O 一氧化二氮</td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td></tr>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">SO₂ 二氧化硫</td><td class="ghg-no"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td></tr>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">HFCs 氫氟碳化物</td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-no"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td></tr>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">PFCs 全氟碳化物</td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-no"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td></tr>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">SF₆ 六氟化硫</td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-no"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td></tr>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">NF₃ 三氟化氮</td><td class="ghg-yes"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-no"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td></tr>
    <tr><td style="text-align:left;padding-left:14px;font-weight:600;">O₃ 臭氧</td><td class="ghg-no"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td><td class="ghg-no"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 臭氧兩者都沒有！台灣管制7種（無SO₂）；IPCC AR6預測用4種（含SO₂，無HFCs/PFCs/SF₆/NF₃）</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch3"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch3-tag">第三章</span><h3>IPCC 三大工作小組</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.ipcc-flow{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
.ipcc-item{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;}
.ipcc-num{width:48px;height:48px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:900;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;}
.ipcc-body{flex:1;padding:10px 12px;font-size:.75rem;line-height:1.6;}
.ipcc-body b{font-size:.82rem;display:block;}
.ipcc-arrow{display:flex;justify-content:center;font-size:.9rem;color:#aaa;}
</style>
<div class="ipcc-flow">
  <div class="ipcc-item">
    <div class="ipcc-num" style="background:#89b4d4;">WG<br>1</div>
    <div class="ipcc-body" style="background:#e8f2f9;">
      <b style="color:#5a8ab8;">物理科學基礎（Physical Science Basis）</b>
      氣候變遷的自然科學基礎：升溫、降水、海平面、極端氣候頻率等
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ipcc-arrow">↓</div>
  <div class="ipcc-item">
    <div class="ipcc-num" style="background:#c87848;">WG<br>2</div>
    <div class="ipcc-body" style="background:#fdf0e0;">
      <b style="color:#b86840;">衝擊、調適與脆弱性（Impacts, Adaptation & Vulnerability）</b>
      氣候變遷對人類社會與生態的衝擊、風險評估與調適策略
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ipcc-arrow">↓</div>
  <div class="ipcc-item">
    <div class="ipcc-num" style="background:#1b5c42;">WG<br>3</div>
    <div class="ipcc-body" style="background:#e2f5ec;">
      <b style="color:#1b5c42;">減緩策略（Mitigation）</b>
      評估各項減碳路徑、技術選擇、政策工具與社會接受度
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> WG1科學基礎 → WG2衝擊調適 → WG3減緩；AR6為第六次評估報告（2021-2022年發布）</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card chart-card-wide" data-ch="ch4"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch4-tag">第四章</span><h3>四大永續債券比較</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.bond-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.78rem;table-layout:auto;}
.bond-tbl th{padding:9px 10px;text-align:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;}
.bond-tbl td{padding:8px 10px;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;line-height:1.5;}
.bond-tbl .bond-label{text-align:left;font-weight:700;color:#37474f;background:#f5f5f5;font-size:.74rem;}
.bond-tbl .bond-slb{background:#fdf0e0;}
.bond-tbl .bond-slb-h{background:#c87848;}
.bond-highlight{color:#c87848;font-weight:800;}
.bond-note{margin-top:10px;background:#e2f5ec;border-left:3px solid #2e7a52;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;padding:8px 12px;font-size:.76rem;color:#2d4a2d;}
</style>
<table class="bond-tbl">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="width:18%;background:#37474f;text-align:left;padding-left:10px;">比較項目</th>
      <th style="background:#2e7a52;">綠色債券</th>
      <th style="background:#89b4d4;">社會責任債券</th>
      <th style="background:#4a9480;">可持續發展債券</th>
      <th class="bond-slb-h">SLB <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg><br><small style="font-weight:400;">可持續發展連結</small></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="bond-label">縮寫準則</td>
      <td>GBP</td>
      <td>SBP</td>
      <td>SBG</td>
      <td class="bond-slb"><b>SLBP</b></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="bond-label">資金用途</td>
      <td>環境專案<br><small>（全數）</small></td>
      <td>社會專案<br><small>（全數）</small></td>
      <td>環境＋社會<br><small>（全數）</small></td>
      <td class="bond-slb"><span class="bond-highlight">用途不限 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span><br><small>一般營運亦可</small></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="bond-label">專款專用</td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></td>
      <td class="bond-slb"><span class="bond-highlight"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg> 不需要</span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="bond-label">KPI / SPT</td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></td>
      <td class="bond-slb"><span class="bond-highlight"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg> 必須設定</span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="bond-label">未達標懲罰</td>
      <td>無（固定利率）</td>
      <td>無（固定利率）</td>
      <td>無（固定利率）</td>
      <td class="bond-slb"><span class="bond-highlight">↑ 加息</span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="bond-label">發行量排行</td>
      <td><b><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89L17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg> 全球最多</b></td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#78909c" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89L17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg></td>
      <td><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#8d6e63" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89L17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg></td>
      <td class="bond-slb">—</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="bond-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg> <b>SLB 核心邏輯</b>：資金用途自由，但須設定永續目標（KPI/SPT）；未達標則 <b>↑ 加息</b>，達標則降息或維持——以利率作為ESG誘因</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> SLB核心是「KPI達標」資金用途不限 ｜ 全球及台灣發行量最大均為綠色債券</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch4"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch4-tag">第四章</span><h3>赤道原則 A / B / C 分級</h3></div><div class="chart-body"><div style="text-align:center;font-size:.8rem;background:#e2f5ec;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;">適用門檻：專案融資金額 ≥ <b style="font-size:1rem;color:#2e7a52">1,000 萬美元</b></div><div class="eq-levels"><div class="eq-lv eq-a"><div class="eq-g">A</div><div class="eq-info"><b>高風險</b> 重大不利、多樣、不可逆<br><span class="eq-req">需環評 + TCFD實體風險</span></div></div><div class="eq-lv eq-b"><div class="eq-g">B</div><div class="eq-info"><b>中風險</b> 影響有限，可減緩<br><span class="eq-req">部分需考慮TCFD實體風險</span></div></div><div class="eq-lv eq-c"><div class="eq-g">C</div><div class="eq-info"><b>低風險</b> 影響輕微或無<br><span class="eq-req">不需環境社會評估</span></div></div></div></div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><line x1="9" y1="18" x2="15" y2="18"/><line x1="10" y1="22" x2="14" y2="22"/><path d="M15.09 14c.18-.98.65-1.74 1.41-2.5A4.65 4.65 0 0 0 18 8 6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .23 2.23 1.5 3.5A4.61 4.61 0 0 1 8.91 14"/></svg> 報告書原則10只針對A類和部分B類，無C類</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch4"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch4-tag">第四章</span><h3>永續金融四大倡議原則</h3></div><div class="chart-body"><div class="im-grid"><div class="im-item im-pri"><div class="im-ico"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><rect x="18" y="3" width="4" height="18"/><rect x="10" y="8" width="4" height="13"/><rect x="2" y="13" width="4" height="8"/></svg></div><div class="im-n">PRI</div><div class="im-f">責任投資原則</div><div class="im-t">投資人</div><div class="im-d">ESG納入投資分析</div></div><div class="im-item im-prb"><div class="im-ico"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="3" y1="22" x2="21" y2="22"/><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6" y2="11"/><line x1="10" y1="18" x2="10" y2="11"/><line x1="14" y1="18" x2="14" y2="11"/><line x1="18" y1="18" x2="18" y2="11"/><polygon points="12 2 20 7 4 7"/></svg></div><div class="im-n">PRB</div><div class="im-f">責任銀行原則</div><div class="im-t">銀行業</div><div class="im-d">策略與巴黎協定一致</div></div><div class="im-item im-psi"><div class="im-ico"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div><div class="im-n">PSI</div><div class="im-f">永續保險原則</div><div class="im-t">保險業</div><div class="im-d">ESG納入核保決策</div></div><div class="im-item im-ep"><div class="im-ico"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="8" rx="1"/><path d="M17 14v7"/><path d="M7 14v7"/><path d="M17 3h.01"/><path d="M7 3h.01"/></svg></div><div class="im-n">EPs</div><div class="im-f">赤道原則</div><div class="im-t">大型專案融資</div><div class="im-d">≥1000萬美元 A/B/C</div></div></div></div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> PRI→投資人，PRB→銀行，PSI→保險，EPs→專案融資</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch4"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch4-tag">第四章</span><h3>ESG 七大投資策略</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.strat-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.76rem;}
.strat-tbl th{padding:6px 8px;color:#fff;font-size:.73rem;text-align:left;}
.strat-tbl td{padding:7px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;vertical-align:top;line-height:1.5;}
.strat-tbl tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}
.strat-num{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:.7rem;flex-shrink:0;}
.strat-key{font-size:.7rem;color:#b71c1c;background:#ffebee;border-radius:4px;padding:1px 6px;}
</style>
<table class="strat-tbl">
  <thead>
    <tr style="background:#37474f;">
      <th style="width:30px;">#</th>
      <th style="width:30%;">策略名稱</th>
      <th>說明 ／ 考點</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td><span class="strat-num" style="background:#c62828">1</span></td>
      <td><b>負向／排除篩選</b></td>
      <td>排除特定負面行業（菸草、武器、博弈、酒精）或違反規範的公司 <span class="strat-key">高頻考</span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><span class="strat-num" style="background:#ad1457">2</span></td>
      <td><b>正向／最佳篩選</b></td>
      <td>選擇同業中ESG表現最佳者；以公信力永續指數為基準判斷</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><span class="strat-num" style="background:#6d4c41">3</span></td>
      <td><b>規範篩選</b></td>
      <td>依UNGC、OECD等國際標準對企業進行篩選，剔除違規者</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><span class="strat-num" style="background:#89b4d4">4</span></td>
      <td><b>ESG整合</b></td>
      <td>將ESG因素融入傳統財務分析；關注公司長期ESG風險與機會</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><span class="strat-num" style="background:#2e7a52">5</span></td>
      <td><b>永續主題投資</b></td>
      <td>聚焦特定主題：潔淨能源、水資源、性別平等、永續農業等 <span class="strat-key"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 高股息不屬此類</span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><span class="strat-num" style="background:#1b5c42">6</span></td>
      <td><b>影響力投資</b></td>
      <td>以投資解決社會／環境問題，<b>同時</b>獲取財務回報（非純慈善） <span class="strat-key">高頻考</span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><span class="strat-num" style="background:#4a9480">7</span></td>
      <td><b>企業參與及股東行動</b></td>
      <td>透過股東身份（投票、議合）影響企業ESG行為；機構投資人主要方式</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><line x1="9" y1="18" x2="15" y2="18"/><line x1="10" y1="22" x2="14" y2="22"/><path d="M15.09 14c.18-.98.65-1.74 1.41-2.5A4.65 4.65 0 0 0 18 8 6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .23 2.23 1.5 3.5A4.61 4.61 0 0 1 8.91 14"/></svg> 影響力投資 ≠ 慈善（需有財務回報）；ESG ETF被動追蹤指數；高股息主題不屬於永續主題投資</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch4"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch4-tag">第四章</span><h3>SFDR 基金分類 (Article 6 / 8 / 9)</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<div class="sfdr-grid">

  <!-- Article 6 -->
  <div class="sfdr-col sfdr-col-6">
    <div class="sfdr-col-head">
      <div class="sfdr-article-num">Article 6</div>
      <div class="sfdr-badge"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#e0e0e0" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="2" fill="#e0e0e0" stroke="none"/></svg> 泛ESG基金</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sfdr-col-body">
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b>定義：</b>僅將永續風險納入考量，揭露屬性未考慮歐盟永續標準</div>
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b>特性：</b>非永續性產品，ESG程度最低</div>
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b>資金用途：</b>不受ESG目標約束</div>
      <div class="sfdr-esg-bar"></div>
      <div class="sfdr-esg-label">ESG程度 20%</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Article 8 -->
  <div class="sfdr-col sfdr-col-8">
    <div class="sfdr-col-head">
      <div class="sfdr-article-num">Article 8</div>
      <div class="sfdr-badge"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#2e7a52" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8" fill="#2e7a52" stroke="none"/></svg> 淺綠基金</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sfdr-col-body">
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b>定義：</b>以促進環境或社會特性為核心，且發行公司治理良好</div>
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b>特性：</b>具備永續投資策略與可促進環境發展之特徵</div>
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 考點：</b>Article 6定義為「泛ESG」，<u>非</u>Article 8</div>
      <div class="sfdr-esg-bar"></div>
      <div class="sfdr-esg-label">ESG程度 60%</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Article 9 -->
  <div class="sfdr-col sfdr-col-9">
    <div class="sfdr-col-head">
      <div class="sfdr-article-num">Article 9</div>
      <div class="sfdr-badge"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 22"/><path d="M2 16s3-1 6-3c3.5-2.3 4.5-5 4.5-5S10 13 8 15c-2.1 2.1-6 3-6 3z"/><path d="M22 2s-5 2-8 7c-2.3 3.5-2 7-2 7s2-3.5 5-6c3.1-2.6 5-8 5-8z"/></svg> 深綠基金 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sfdr-col-body">
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b>定義：</b>以實現永續投資為核心目標</div>
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b>條件：</b>經評估確認可對環境/社會帶來貢獻，且未造成主要不利影響 (PAIs)</div>
      <div class="sfdr-col-row"><b>ESG程度：</b>最高級別</div>
      <div class="sfdr-esg-bar"></div>
      <div class="sfdr-esg-label">ESG程度 100%</div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
<div class="sfdr-arrow"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#e0e0e0" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="2" fill="#e0e0e0" stroke="none"/></svg> Article 6 &nbsp;→&nbsp; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#2e7a52" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8" fill="#2e7a52" stroke="none"/></svg> Article 8 &nbsp;→&nbsp; <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 22"/><path d="M2 16s3-1 6-3c3.5-2.3 4.5-5 4.5-5S10 13 8 15c-2.1 2.1-6 3-6 3z"/><path d="M22 2s-5 2-8 7c-2.3 3.5-2 7-2 7s2-3.5 5-6c3.1-2.6 5-8 5-8z"/></svg> Article 9 &nbsp;&nbsp;（ESG 程度遞增）</div>
<div class="sfdr-must"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="#d4a56a" stroke="none" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg> 考點：真正落實ESG精神的基金，至少必須符合 <b>Article 8</b> 或 <b>Article 9</b></div>

</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><line x1="9" y1="18" x2="15" y2="18"/><line x1="10" y1="22" x2="14" y2="22"/><path d="M15.09 14c.18-.98.65-1.74 1.41-2.5A4.65 4.65 0 0 0 18 8 6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .23 2.23 1.5 3.5A4.61 4.61 0 0 1 8.91 14"/></svg> Article 6 = 泛ESG（非永續性）；Article 8 = 淺綠；Article 9 = 深綠最高級 ｜ 真正ESG需符合8或9</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch4"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch4-tag">第四章</span><h3>永續授信三大工具比較</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.sl-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.75rem;}
.sl-tbl th{padding:7px 8px;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:.72rem;text-align:center;}
.sl-tbl td{padding:7px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0;vertical-align:top;line-height:1.5;text-align:center;}
.sl-tbl tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}
.sl-tbl .sl-label{text-align:left;font-weight:600;color:#546e7a;font-size:.72rem;width:72px;}
.sl-key{font-size:.68rem;color:#b71c1c;background:#ffebee;border-radius:4px;padding:1px 5px;}
</style>
<table class="sl-tbl">
  <thead><tr>
    <th style="background:#455a64;text-align:left;padding-left:10px;">項目</th>
    <th style="background:#2e7a52;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 22"/><path d="M2 16s3-1 6-3c3.5-2.3 4.5-5 4.5-5S10 13 8 15c-2.1 2.1-6 3-6 3z"/><path d="M22 2s-5 2-8 7c-2.3 3.5-2 7-2 7s2-3.5 5-6c3.1-2.6 5-8 5-8z"/></svg> 綠色貸款（GL）</th>
    <th style="background:#89b4d4;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg> 永續連結貸款（SLL）</th>
    <th style="background:#8872b8;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/><polyline points="1 20 1 14 7 14"/><path d="M3.51 9a9 9 0 0 1 14.85-3.36L23 10M1 14l4.64 4.36A9 9 0 0 0 20.49 15"/></svg> 轉型貸款</th>
  </tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td class="sl-label" style="text-align:left;padding-left:10px;">資金用途</td><td><b>限定</b>綠色專案</td><td><b>不限定</b>（任何用途）<span class="sl-key"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 考點</span></td><td>高碳排產業轉型</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="sl-label" style="text-align:left;padding-left:10px;">利率機制</td><td>固定優惠利率</td><td>KPI達成→降息<br>未達成→<b>升息</b></td><td>與轉型計畫掛鉤</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="sl-label" style="text-align:left;padding-left:10px;">KPI</td><td>無</td><td>必須設定 SPT<span class="sl-key">必考</span></td><td>轉型目標</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="sl-label" style="text-align:left;padding-left:10px;">ICMA準則</td><td>GLP</td><td>SLLP</td><td>CLG</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> SLL 核心：資金用途「不限定」但利率浮動；SPT未達標則利率 Step-up（升息）</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card chart-card-wide" data-ch="ch4"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch4-tag">第四章</span><h3>漂綠 vs 非漂綠：常見情境對照</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.gw-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;}
.gw-col{border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;}
.gw-head{padding:8px 14px;font-weight:800;font-size:.82rem;color:#fff;}
.gw-body{padding:10px 12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;}
.gw-row{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:.74rem;line-height:1.5;}
.gw-icon{flex-shrink:0;font-size:.9rem;}
.gw-yes .gw-head{background:#c62828;}
.gw-yes .gw-body{background:#ffebee;}
.gw-no .gw-head{background:#1b5c42;}
.gw-no .gw-body{background:#e2f5ec;}
</style>
<div class="gw-grid">
  <div class="gw-col gw-yes">
    <div class="gw-head"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M11.5 2C6.81 2 3 5.81 3 10.5S6.81 19 11.5 19h1V22h-5v-2.5c-2.5-1-5-4.5-5-9C2.5 4.75 6.75 1 12 1s9.5 3.75 9.5 9.5c0 4.5-2.5 8-5 9V22h-5v-3h1c4.69 0 8.5-3.81 8.5-8.5S17.19 2 11.5 2z"/></svg> 涉及漂綠</div>
    <div class="gw-body">
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span><div>聲稱「百分百綠色」但實際只有部分業務符合</div></div>
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span><div>永續報告書只揭露正面表現，隱瞞負面衝擊</div></div>
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span><div>使用「天然」「環保」等模糊詞語，無第三方認證</div></div>
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c62828" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg></span><div>強調某項環保優點，但隱藏其他重大負面衝擊</div></div>
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg></span><div>基金銷售頁同時包含永續與一般商品，未清楚區分</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="gw-col gw-no">
    <div class="gw-head"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg> 不涉及漂綠</div>
    <div class="gw-body">
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><div>完整揭露環境影響，包含正面與負面</div></div>
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><div>永續聲明有具體數據與第三方驗證支持</div></div>
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><div>對永續商品與一般商品清楚標示區分</div></div>
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><div>揭露達成目標的困難與限制</div></div>
      <div class="gw-row"><span class="gw-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></span><div>聲明直接易懂，不模糊不清</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 防漂綠五大原則：①真實有據 ②直接易懂 ③完整不遺漏 ④比較公平 ⑤符合永續規範</div></div>
      <div class="chart-card" data-ch="ch4"><div class="chart-card-header"><span class="chart-tag ch4-tag">第四章</span><h3>永續保險商品四大類型</h3></div><div class="chart-body">
<style>
.ins-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;}
.ins-box{border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;}
.ins-head{padding:8px 12px;font-weight:800;font-size:.78rem;color:#fff;}
.ins-body{padding:9px 12px;font-size:.73rem;line-height:1.6;}
.ins-body li{margin-bottom:2px;}
.ins-trap{font-size:.68rem;color:#b71c1c;background:#ffebee;border-radius:4px;padding:1px 6px;display:inline-block;margin-top:4px;}
@media(max-width:480px){.ins-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
</style>
<div class="ins-grid">
  <div class="ins-box">
    <div class="ins-head" style="background:#2e7a52;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#2e7a52" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><rect x="1" y="6" width="18" height="12" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="23" y1="13" x2="23" y2="11"/><line x1="5" y1="10" x2="5" y2="14"/><line x1="10" y1="10" x2="10" y2="14"/></svg> 再生能源保險</div>
    <div class="ins-body" style="background:#e2f5ec;">
      保障再生能源設備於<b>建造</b>及<b>營運</b>中的損失<br>
      • 離岸風電、太陽能、水力（無地熱）<br>
      • 含延遲開工損失、恐怖主義損失<br>
      <span class="ins-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 不需能源服務業者</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ins-box">
    <div class="ins-head" style="background:#89b4d4;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;" ><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg> 綠建築保險</div>
    <div class="ins-body" style="background:#e8f2f9;">
      損失後可選擇升級為<b>綠色建材/綠建築</b><br>
      三種類型：<br>
      • 重置成本保障型<br>
      • 相關費用保障型<br>
      • 營業中斷保障型
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ins-box">
    <div class="ins-head" style="background:#c88a50;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="8" y1="13" x2="8" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M20 16.58A5 5 0 0 0 18 7h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 4 15.25"/></svg> 參數型天氣保險</div>
    <div class="ins-body" style="background:#fdf4e3;">
      以<b>客觀氣象指標</b>觸發理賠（非損失觸發）<br>
      降水量、風速、溫度等參數達標即賠<br>
      優點：快速理賠、道德風險低<br>
      <span class="ins-trap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 基差風險是缺點</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="ins-box">
    <div class="ins-head" style="background:#8872b8;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"/><polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg> 節能/綠色汽車保險</div>
    <div class="ins-body" style="background:#ede8f7;">
      UBI 保險：以<b>里程計算保費</b><br>
      電動車/油電車：給予保費折扣<br>
      節能保險：能源服務業者無法達到節能目標時由保險公司賠償
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="chart-note"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#c88a50" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg> 地震保險不屬於綠色保險；參數型保險 = 指標觸發（非損失觸發）</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div><!-- /page-charts -->
